<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.1.2">
<l>kōṭpaṭṭa cintaiyāyk kūrvāya vaṉṟilē</l>
<l>cēṭpaṭṭa yāmaṅkaḷ cērā tiraṅkutiyā</l>
<l>lāṭpaṭṭa vemmēpō ṉīyu maravaṇaiyāṉ</l>
<l>ṟāṭpaṭṭa taṇṭuḻāyt tāmaṅkā muṟṟāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You whose mind has been captured, sharp-mouthed Aṉṟil,</l>
<l>you will cry without joining distant midnights.</l>
<l>Enslaved like us you too desire the cool Tulsi string</l> 
<l>from the foot of the one on the serpent bed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
